{"type":"message","id":"a40f28ad","parentId":"0f1ae346","timestamp":"2026-03-24T18:40:22.151Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_5yjntwp9946r_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Pulse: 2026-03-24 143941\n\n## Applied Mutations\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\nRejected: the (missing)\n\n## LLM Response\n<think>\r\nLet me analyze the current state based on the provided context:\r\n\r\n1. Last pulse was pulse_2026-03-24 143841.md\r\n2. Key pending task: Hybrid CFIxFreq scoring experiment (Strategy C)\r\n   - Formula: score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120)\r\n   - Test if this distinguishes \"constant format\" (freq�160, CFI=1) from \"research trajectory\" (freq<120, CFI>0.5)\r\n   - Run: 200 pulses, 80/20 split, compare against binary thresholds\r\n\r\n3. The notes indicate:\r\n   - \"No mutations applied this cycle\"\r\n   - Key insight: Need THREE-DIMENSIONAL filter: CFI � 0.5 AND freq ? [3, 120)\r\n   - Compression objective: score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120)\r\n\r\nI need to advance the pending experiment. Let me check if there's any prior experiment code or data I can build upon.\r\n\r\nLooking at the research directory mentioned:\r\n- `research/CFI_COMPRESSION_SYNTHESIS.md` - contains the full experiment comparing freq-only vs CFI-hard\r\n\r\nI should:\r\n1. Look at the existing experiment code/data\r\n2. Design and implement the hybrid scoring experiment\r\n\r\nLet me check what files exist that I can work with.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe hybrid CFIxFreq scoring experiment (Strategy C) is the next critical step to advance compression research. The formula `score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120)` needs validation against the binary threshold approaches tested in the prior experiment.\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nCreate the experiment script for Strategy C: Hybrid CFIxFreq scoring. This will test if the multiplicative formula distinguishes constant-format tokens (freq�160, CFI=1) from research trajectory tokens (freq<120, CFI>0.5) better than binary thresholds.\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n`\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # CFIxFreq Hybrid Scoring Experiment (Strategy C)\r\n# Testing: score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120)\r\n# Compare against binary thresholds from prior experiment\r\n\r\n$STOP = 200\r\n\r\n# Load pulse data from prior experiment\r\n$dataPath = \"research/cfi_pulse_data.json\"\r\nif (Test-Path $dataPath) {\r\n    $pulses = Get-Content $dataPath | ConvertFrom-Json\r\n} else {\r\n    Write-Host \"[ERROR] Missing: $dataPath - run prior CFI experiment first\"\r\n    exit 1\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Strategy C: Hybrid scoring formula\r\nfunction Get-HybridScore {\r\n    param($cfi, $freq)\r\n    $freqNorm = [Math]::Min(1, $freq / 120)\r\n    return $cfi * $freqNorm\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Classify with each strategy\r\n$results = @()\r\nforeach ($p in $pulses) {\r\n    $hybrid = Get-HybridScore -cfi $p.CFI -freq $p.Freq\r\n    \r\n    # Thresholds from prior experiment\r\n    $cfiHard = ($p.CFI -ge 0.7 -and $p.Freq -lt 60)\r\n    $freqOnly = ($p.Freq -ge 3 -and $p.Freq -lt 60)\r\n    \r\n    $results += [PSCustomObject]@{\r\n        PulseId = $p.PulseId\r\n        CFI = $p.CFI\r\n        Freq = $p.Freq\r\n        HybridScore = $hybrid\r\n        Hybrid_Qualifies = ($hybrid -ge 0.5)\r\n        CFIHard = $cfiHard\r\n        FreqOnly = $freqOnly\r\n        IsSignal = $p.IsSignal\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Precision/Recall analysis\r\n$hybridTP = ($results | Where-Object { $_.Hybrid_Qualifies -and $_.IsSignal }).Count\r\n$hybridFP = ($results | Where-Object { $_.Hybrid_Qualifies -and -not $_.IsSignal }).Count\r\n$hybridTN = ($results | Where-Object { -not $_.Hybrid_Qualifies -and -not $_.IsSignal }).Count\r\n$hybridFN = ($results | Where-Object { -not $_.Hybrid_Qualifies -and $_.IsSignal }).Count\r\n\r\n$hybridPrec = if (($hybridTP + $hybridFP) -gt 0) { $hybridTP / ($hybridTP + $hybridFP) } else { 0 }\r\n$hybridRec = if (($hybridTP + $hybridFN) -gt 0) { $hybridTP / ($hybridTP + $hybridFN) } else { 0 }\r\n$hybridF1 = if (($hybridPrec + $hybridRec) -gt 0) { 2 * $hybridPrec * $hybridRec / ($hybridPrec + $hybridRec) } else { 0 }\r\n\r\n# Compare strategies\r\nWrite-Host \"=== Strategy Comparison ===\"\r\nWrite-Host \"Strategy C (Hybrid): P=$([math]::Round($hybridPrec,4)) R=$([math]::Round($hybridRec,4)) F1=$([math]::Round($hybridF1,4))\"\r\n\r\n# Identify problematic constant-format tokens (should score LOW with hybrid)\r\n$constants = $results | Where-Object { $_.Freq -ge 150 -and $_.CFI -ge 0.95 }\r\nWrite-Host \"`n=== Constant-Format Tokens (freq�150, CFI�0.95) ===\"\r\nWrite-Host \"Count: $($constants.Count)\"\r\n$constants | Sort-Object HybridScore | Select-Object -First 5 | Format-Table Freq, CFI, HybridScore\r\n\r\n# Key test: Do constants score lower than research\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 14:40:00"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":667,"aggregated":"# Pulse: 2026-03-24 143941\n\n## Applied Mutations\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\nRejected: the (missing)\n\n## LLM Response\n<think>\r\nLet me analyze the current state based on the provided context:\r\n\r\n1. Last pulse was pulse_2026-03-24 143841.md\r\n2. Key pending task: Hybrid CFIxFreq scoring experiment (Strategy C)\r\n   - Formula: score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120)\r\n   - Test if this distinguishes \"constant format\" (freq�160, CFI=1) from \"research trajectory\" (freq<120, CFI>0.5)\r\n   - Run: 200 pulses, 80/20 split, compare against binary thresholds\r\n\r\n3. The notes indicate:\r\n   - \"No mutations applied this cycle\"\r\n   - Key insight: Need THREE-DIMENSIONAL filter: CFI � 0.5 AND freq ? [3, 120)\r\n   - Compression objective: score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120)\r\n\r\nI need to advance the pending experiment. Let me check if there's any prior experiment code or data I can build upon.\r\n\r\nLooking at the research directory mentioned:\r\n- `research/CFI_COMPRESSION_SYNTHESIS.md` - contains the full experiment comparing freq-only vs CFI-hard\r\n\r\nI should:\r\n1. Look at the existing experiment code/data\r\n2. Design and implement the hybrid scoring experiment\r\n\r\nLet me check what files exist that I can work with.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe hybrid CFIxFreq scoring experiment (Strategy C) is the next critical step to advance compression research. The formula `score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120)` needs validation against the binary threshold approaches tested in the prior experiment.\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nCreate the experiment script for Strategy C: Hybrid CFIxFreq scoring. This will test if the multiplicative formula distinguishes constant-format tokens (freq�160, CFI=1) from research trajectory tokens (freq<120, CFI>0.5) better than binary thresholds.\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n`\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # CFIxFreq Hybrid Scoring Experiment (Strategy C)\r\n# Testing: score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120)\r\n# Compare against binary thresholds from prior experiment\r\n\r\n$STOP = 200\r\n\r\n# Load pulse data from prior experiment\r\n$dataPath = \"research/cfi_pulse_data.json\"\r\nif (Test-Path $dataPath) {\r\n    $pulses = Get-Content $dataPath | ConvertFrom-Json\r\n} else {\r\n    Write-Host \"[ERROR] Missing: $dataPath - run prior CFI experiment first\"\r\n    exit 1\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Strategy C: Hybrid scoring formula\r\nfunction Get-HybridScore {\r\n    param($cfi, $freq)\r\n    $freqNorm = [Math]::Min(1, $freq / 120)\r\n    return $cfi * $freqNorm\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Classify with each strategy\r\n$results = @()\r\nforeach ($p in $pulses) {\r\n    $hybrid = Get-HybridScore -cfi $p.CFI -freq $p.Freq\r\n    \r\n    # Thresholds from prior experiment\r\n    $cfiHard = ($p.CFI -ge 0.7 -and $p.Freq -lt 60)\r\n    $freqOnly = ($p.Freq -ge 3 -and $p.Freq -lt 60)\r\n    \r\n    $results += [PSCustomObject]@{\r\n        PulseId = $p.PulseId\r\n        CFI = $p.CFI\r\n        Freq = $p.Freq\r\n        HybridScore = $hybrid\r\n        Hybrid_Qualifies = ($hybrid -ge 0.5)\r\n        CFIHard = $cfiHard\r\n        FreqOnly = $freqOnly\r\n        IsSignal = $p.IsSignal\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Precision/Recall analysis\r\n$hybridTP = ($results | Where-Object { $_.Hybrid_Qualifies -and $_.IsSignal }).Count\r\n$hybridFP = ($results | Where-Object { $_.Hybrid_Qualifies -and -not $_.IsSignal }).Count\r\n$hybridTN = ($results | Where-Object { -not $_.Hybrid_Qualifies -and -not $_.IsSignal }).Count\r\n$hybridFN = ($results | Where-Object { -not $_.Hybrid_Qualifies -and $_.IsSignal }).Count\r\n\r\n$hybridPrec = if (($hybridTP + $hybridFP) -gt 0) { $hybridTP / ($hybridTP + $hybridFP) } else { 0 }\r\n$hybridRec = if (($hybridTP + $hybridFN) -gt 0) { $hybridTP / ($hybridTP + $hybridFN) } else { 0 }\r\n$hybridF1 = if (($hybridPrec + $hybridRec) -gt 0) { 2 * $hybridPrec * $hybridRec / ($hybridPrec + $hybridRec) } else { 0 }\r\n\r\n# Compare strategies\r\nWrite-Host \"=== Strategy Comparison ===\"\r\nWrite-Host \"Strategy C (Hybrid): P=$([math]::Round($hybridPrec,4)) R=$([math]::Round($hybridRec,4)) F1=$([math]::Round($hybridF1,4))\"\r\n\r\n# Identify problematic constant-format tokens (should score LOW with hybrid)\r\n$constants = $results | Where-Object { $_.Freq -ge 150 -and $_.CFI -ge 0.95 }\r\nWrite-Host \"`n=== Constant-Format Tokens (freq�150, CFI�0.95) ===\"\r\nWrite-Host \"Count: $($constants.Count)\"\r\n$constants | Sort-Object HybridScore | Select-Object -First 5 | Format-Table Freq, CFI, HybridScore\r\n\r\n# Key test: Do constants score lower than research\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 14:40:00","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774377622149}}
